<node TEXT="【MR6267】" FOLDED="true" ID="ID_941994621" CREATED="1584335888502" MODIFIED="1594793732368" LINK="https://lte-wiki.rnd.ki.sw.ericsson.se/wiki/MR6267_Allow_TTI_bundling_parameters_to_be_changed_in_runtime(Global_Release)"><richcontent TYPE="NOTE">

<html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      <b><font color="#0000c0">MR ID:</font></b>
    </p>
    <p>
      105 65-0937/06267
    </p>
    <p>
      
    </p>
    <p>
      <b><font color="#0000c0">MR Title:</font></b>
    </p>
    <p>
      Allow TTI bundling parameters to be changed in runtime
    </p>
    <p>
      
    </p>
    <p>
      <b><font color="#0000c0">Requirement Text:</font></b>
    </p>
    <p>
      Allow the two parameters to be changed without making lock/unlock.
    </p>
    <p>
      -ttiBundlingSwitchThres
    </p>
    <p>
      -ttiBundlingSwitchThresHyst
    </p>
    <p>
      
    </p>
    <p>
      <b><font color="#0000c0">Rationale:</font></b>
    </p>
    <p>
      SON-OM has a feature that adjusts the TTI bundling parameters to an optimum and currently they require lock/unlock in order to take effect. This undermines the efficiency and possibility to utilize the SON-OM product.
    </p>
    <p>
      
    </p>
    <p>
      <b><font color="#0000c0">Customers:</font></b>
    </p>
    <p>
      Verizon MRD
    </p>
    <p>
      Vfe UK MRD
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
</richcontent>
